An [`Object`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object) with two properties:

[`done`](#done)

A boolean value:

*   `true` if the generator function's control flow has reached the end.
*   `false` if the generator function's control flow hasn't reached the end and can produce more values. This can only happen if the `return` is captured in a [`try...finally`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/try...catch#the_finally_block) and there are more `yield` expressions in the `finally` block.

